Emirates Telecommunications Corp.,
known as Etisalat, submitted a preliminary “conditional offer”
for a stake in Kuwait’s Mobile Telecommunications Co., known as
Zain, according to Etisalat’s spokesman Ahmed bin Ali.  To contact the reporter on this story:
